e as many \\MJ\\ and GERDA collaborators have joined with\nscientists from other efforts to give birth to the LEGEND collaboration. LEGEND\nwill exploit the best features of both experiments to extend the half-life\nlimit beyond $10^{28}$ yr with a ton-scale experiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 16:16:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
