lso be adapted to the\ncase where communication between the user and each server is through a\nlinearly-coded network, achieving the same rate as previous known PIR schemes\nbut with polynomial field sizes in the number of servers, instead of\nexponential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 21:42:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 15:55:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-17"}
