brane is also observed due to\nadditional phonon membrane boundary scattering. The impact of the\nGa2O3substrate TBC and substrate thermal conductivity on the thermal\nperformance of a power device are modeled and discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 22:44:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-11"}
