s in pro-$p$ groups.\n  The results about full Hausdorff spectra hold more generally for finite\ndirect products of finitely generated pro-$p$ groups of positive rank gradient\nand for mixed finite direct products of finitely generated non-abelian free\npro-$p$ groups and non-soluble Demushkin groups, respectively. Analogously, the\naforementioned results with respect to the Frattini series generalise further\nto Hausdorff dimension functions with respect to arbitrary iterated verbal\nfiltrations. Finally, we determine the normal Hausdorff spectra of such direct\nproducts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 11:11:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 21:04:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 31 Oct 2019 07:54:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-27"}
