olution for large initial data provided that\nthe initial data are radially symmetric and sufficiently regular in dimension\n$N=2,3$ for $\\gamma$ law pressure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 13:16:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-11"}
