ly the number of baseline\npermutations and motivates the use of more interferometers for round the clock\ncoverage of all repeat events of a given source, in order to maximise the\norbital details and sky localization of lensed BBH sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 14:27:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-11"}
