ion. Our analyses indicate that Anderson lattices\nwith appropriate spin-orbit interactions provide a platform for realizing all\ntypes of topological semi-metallic phase\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 14:27:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Jan 2019 14:34:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-29"}
